\id 2JN  
\h 2 Yuhanna 
\toc1 ∆Āataaki Yuhanna …ói…óa…ďo 
\toc2 2 Yuhanna 
\toc3 2Yn. 
\mt1 ∆Āataaki Yuhanna …ói…óa…ďo 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Miin maw…óo deental goon…óin…ďe winndi oo …ďataaki faade e debbo teddu…óo\f + \fr 1:1 \fk Debbo teddu…óo oo \ft e …ďi…ď…ďe mum yo deental goon…óin…ďe gootal.\f* mo Laam…óo su…ďii. Mi…óo jowte, aan e …ďi…ď…ďe maa fuu, onon …ďe nji…óir-mi goonga. Wanaa miin tan yi…ói on, anndu…ďe goonga oo …ďee fuu ana nji…óiri on  
\v 2 saabe goonga gon…óo e men, duumotoo…óo e men faa abada oo.  
\v 3 Laam…óo \w Baabiraa…óo\w* men e \w ∆Āiyum\w* Iisaa \w Almasiihu\w* yurmoto en, hokkan en mo∆ī∆īere e jam kammari goonga e jilli. 
\s1 Haala goonga e jilli 
\p  
\v 4 Mi seyike sanne ko kumpitii-mi won …ďi…ď…ďe maa jokkir…ďe goonga oo no \w Baabiraa…óo\w* yamiri en nii.  
\v 5 Jooni, debbo teddu…óo, mi…óo ndaarde, nji…óondiren. Ko mbinndanan-maa-mi koo wanaa yamiroore heyre, …óum yamiroore nde ke…ďu-…óen gila arannde.  
\v 6 Ko woni jilli dee, haybude jamirooje Laam…óo. Nden yamiroore woni nde kaan-…óon haybirde no nanir-…óon …óum gila arannde nii.  
\v 7 Sabi majjinoo…ďe heew…ďe caakike e aduna oo. ∆Āe nja…ďaali Iisaa \w Almasiihu\w* warii laatike ne…ó…óo. Baa…óo no ma…ď…ďe nii fuu yo majjinoowo yo konnee-Almasiihu.  
\v 8 Kaybee ko'e mon, pati golle mo ngollu-…óon oo mursee, ke…ďon mbarjaari ki…ď…ďundi.  
\v 9 Sabi mo …≤ii…ďaali e laawol Almasiihu ngol, walanaa Laam…óo. ∆Ěii…ďu…óo e maggol ana woodani Baabiraa…óo e \w Bajjo\w* oo fuu.  
\v 10 So won gar…óo e mon ana waajoo ko waldaa e laawol ngol, pati nja…ď…ďee …óum e ley galleeji mon, pati fay njowtee …óum.  
\v 11 Sabi jowtu…óo mo fuu, ka…≤um e makko laatike gootum. 
\s1 Baynondiral 
\p  
\v 12 Ko kaan-mi haalande on koo ana heewi, mi yi…óaa winndande on …óum fuu e …óerewol. Kaa mi…óo yeloo warde to mon, kaalden hunduko e hunduko, yalla seyo men ana hi…ď…ďa. 
\p  
\v 13 Haya, …ďi…ď…ďe sakiike maa debbo mo Laam…óo su…ďii oo ana njowte.